arStrings.szText: Kills extend the duration of your active {c_important}Touch of Death{/c} swarms by {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0"|1|]{/c} seconds. When a swarm is replaced early it bursts for {c_random}[Affix_Value_1*100|%|]{/c} of the damage it would have done.
